#: svelte/contribute/Area.svelte:14 svelte/contribute/Header.svelte:16 svelte/contribute/Header.svelte:18 svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:14
msgid "Contribute"
msgstr "Sodelujte"

#: svelte/contribute/Area.svelte:14 svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:14
msgid "Mozilla Support"
msgstr "Podpora Mozilla"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:55
msgid "Support forum"
msgstr "Forum za podporo"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:63 svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:117 svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:173
msgid "Learn the basic guidelines"
msgstr "Spoznajte osnovne smernice"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:70
msgid "Find support questions to answer"
msgstr "Poiščite vprašanja, na katera lahko odgovorite"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:73
msgid "Start answering!"
msgstr "Začnite odgovarjati!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:78
msgid "Learn more about forum contribution"
msgstr "Več o sodelovanju na forumu"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:85
msgid "1 → 1000"
msgstr "1 → 1000"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:86
msgid "Solving one issue helps up to 1000 users a day"
msgstr "Ena rešena težava lahko vsak dan pomaga tisočem"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:92 svelte/contribute/Picker.svelte:25
msgid "Answer questions in the support forum"
msgstr "Odgovarjajte na vprašanja na forumu za podporo"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:93
msgid "Where all the action happens"
msgstr "Kjer je akcija"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:95
msgid ""
"From hardcore web developers to \"how do I install Firefox\"\n"
"                    first time users, everybody needs your help in the forum!\n"
"                    Share your knowledge by pointing people to the right help\n"
"                    articles and providing troubleshooting steps for their\n"
"                    individual questions."
msgstr ""
"zagrizenih spletnih razvijalcev do novincev z vprašanji tipa \"kako\n"
"                    namestiti Firefox\", vsi potrebujejo vašo pomoč na forumu!\n"
"                    Delite svoje znanje, usmerite ljudi na prave članke s pomočjo,\n"
"                    pomagajte jim odpraviti težave in ponudite individualizirane\n"
"                    odgovore na njihova vprašanja."

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:105
msgid "Help articles"
msgstr "Članki s pomočjo"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:124
msgid "Explore the Knowledge Base Dashboard"
msgstr "Raziščite pregledno ploščo zbirke znanja"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:133
msgid "Check the Needs Update column and start editing articles!"
msgstr "Preverite stolpec „Potrebna posodobitev“ in začnite urejati članke!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:142
msgid "Learn more about KB contribution"
msgstr "Več o prispevanju v zbirko znanja"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:147 svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:203
msgid "400 → 70+"
msgstr "400 → 70+"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:148 svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:204
msgid "One article can be viewed by 400 million users and translated into 70+ languages"
msgstr "En članek lahko prebere 400 milijonov uporabnikov, lahko v več kot 70 jezikih"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:154
msgid "Help us write help articles"
msgstr "Pomagajte nam pri pisanju člankov s pomočjo"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:155
msgid "Share your wisdom with the world!"
msgstr "Delite svoje znanje s svetom!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:157
msgid ""
"If you like writing and teaching, then the Knowledge Base (KB) is the place for you. We need contributors that can write, edit or proofread articles in English. Thousands of people are accessing "
"our Knowledge Base every week. Imagine how many will be helped by you!"
msgstr ""
"Če radi pišete in poučujete, je zbirka znanja (KB) pravi kraj za vas. Potrebujemo sodelavce, ki znajo pisati, urejati in popravljati članke. Vsak teden na tisoče uporabnikov išče po zbirki znanja. "
"Samo pomislite, koliko ljudem boste lahko pomagali!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:165
msgid "Localization"
msgstr "Lokalizacija"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:180
msgid "Check if your locale is available and go to your localization dashboard"
msgstr "Obiščite slovensko pregledno ploščo za lokalizacijo"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:189
msgid "Start localizing an article!"
msgstr "Začnite lokalizirati članek!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:196
msgid "Learn more about localization contribution"
msgstr "Več o sodelovanju pri lokalizaciji"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:210
msgid "Help us localize support articles"
msgstr "Pomagajte nam pri lokalizaciji člankov za podporo"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:212
msgid "Let’s make Mozilla Support speak your language!"
msgstr "Pomagajte Podpori Mozilla govoriti slovensko!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:215
msgid "Help articles are not available in your language yet? You want to join the amazing team translating them? You will help millions of users in your language. Pretty heroic, right?"
msgstr "Članki še niso objavljeni v slovenščini? Bi se pridružili slovenski ekipi za lokalizacijo? Slovenski uporabniki Firefoxa vam bodo hvaležni. Prav junaško, kajne?"

#: svelte/contribute/Header.svelte:13
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Začetna stran"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:18
msgid "Save the world from the comfort of your couch"
msgstr "Rešite svet iz udobja svojega kavča"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:21
msgid "Help millions of users get the most out of their favorite browser. Your contributions will reach millions of users worldwide, and you can do it from the comfort of your couch!"
msgstr ""
"Pomagajte milijonom uporabnikov, da iz svojega najljubšega brskalnika iztisnejo čim več. Vaši prispevki bodo dosegli milijone uporabnikov po vsem svetu, sestavljate pa jih lahko udobno na svojem "
"kavču!"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:26
msgid "We need your help!"
msgstr "Potrebujemo vašo pomoč!"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:29
msgid "Used by more than 400 million people, Mozilla support is fully powered by volunteers, and it’s more important than ever. This is where you come in."
msgstr "Mozillina podpora, ki jo uporablja več kot 400 milijonov ljudi, je v celoti v rokah prostovoljcev in je pomembnejša kot kdajkoli prej. Sedaj ste vi na vrsti."

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:39
msgid "About us"
msgstr "O nas"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:41
msgid "Mozilla Support is a community of enthusiastic volunteers and employees trying to support our users around the globe. Join us for an incredible adventure!"
msgstr ""
"Podpora Mozilla (SuMo) je skupnost navdušenih prostovoljcev in zaposlenih, ki skušajo po svojih najboljših močeh podpirati uporabnike po vsem svetu. Pridružite se nam pri tej neverjetni avanturi!"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:54
msgid "Photo of Mozilla staff and volunteers."
msgstr "Fotografija Mozillinih zaposlenih in prostovoljcev."

#: svelte/contribute/Picker.svelte:16
msgid "Other ways to contribute"
msgstr "Drugi načini sodelovanja"

#: svelte/contribute/Picker.svelte:18
msgid "Pick a way to contribute"
msgstr "Izberite, kako želite sodelovati"

#: svelte/contribute/Picker.svelte:30
msgid "Write help articles"
msgstr "Pišite članke s pomočjo"

#: svelte/contribute/Picker.svelte:35
msgid "Localize support content"
msgstr "Lokalizirajte članke za podporo"

#: svelte/contribute/Steps.svelte:31
msgid "How you can contribute"
msgstr "Kako lahko prispevate"

#: svelte/contribute/Steps.svelte:38
msgid "Sign up as a volunteer"
msgstr "Registrirajte se kot prostovoljec"

#: svelte/contribute/Steps.svelte:42
msgid "Take the contributor's CPG training."
msgstr "Udeležite se usposabljanja CPG."
